%head
	%title
	:css
		@media only screen and (max-width:620px){
			img {
				max-width:100% !important;
			}
			#inner-body {
				width:100% !important;
				max-width:620px !important;
			}
		}
%body
	%table#body-container{:height => "100%", :width => "100%", :style => "border-collapse: collapse;"}
		%tr
			%td{:align => "center", :valign => "top"}
				%table#inner-body{:width => "620", :cellspacing => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :style => "border-spacing:0;border-collapse: collapse;"}
					%tr
						%td{:align => "center", :valign => "top"}
							%table{:style => "margin: 0;padding: 0;max-width: 620px;width: 100%;"}
								%tr{:style => "margin: 0;padding: 0;"}
									%td{:style => "margin: 0;padding: 0;"}
										%p{:style => "margin: 0;padding: 10px 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;font-size: 11px;line-height: 1;"} 
											%span{:style => "color:#70bf4c"}Uruut. 
											Connect. Cooperate. Take Action
					%tr
						%td{:align => "center", :valign => "top"}
							%table#email-header{:bgcolor => "#403e37", :width => "100%", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border-spacing:0;border-collapse: collapse;"}
								%tr
									%td{:align => "left", :valign => "top", :style => "border-bottom:6px solid #70bf4c;"}
										%img{:src => "https://uruut.herokuapp.com/assets/logo.png", :style => "margin:10px;display:block;"}
									%td{:align => "right", :valign => "top", :style => "border-bottom:6px solid #70bf4c;"}
										%a{:href => "http://#{@host}/users/sign_in"}
											%img{:src => "http://#{@host}/assets/email-login.png", :style => "display:block;margin:25px 10px 0 0;"}
					%tr
						%td{:valign => "top"}
							%img{:src => "https://www.uruut.com/assets/pr-email-banner.jpg", :style => "display:block;"}
					%tr
						%td{:valign => "top"}
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								Dear #{@name},
								
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								Welcome to Uruut!  You are one step closer to a more vibrant community where "Strengthening Community Starts With U."
								
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								Uruut helps transform communities by bringing individuals, businesses and foundations together with groups seeking community-level funding through a transparent, feature-rich, crowdfunding platform.
								
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								We are very excited to have you as part of the Uruut Community!
								
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								You can find out more about Uruut and our innovative, new approach to crowdfunding 
								%a{:href => "https://uruut.herokuapp.com/pages/funding_sources"} here
								, and you can browse our projects in the 
								%a{:href => "https://uruut.herokuapp.com/browse/projects"} Marketplace
								.
								  
							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								Please follow us Facebook and Twitter by using the links below.  If you are interested in setting up a project of your own, or need more information, please <link to contact us>.

							%p{:style => "color:#444;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:14px;"}
								Welcome!
								%br
								The Uruut Team
								
					%tr
						%td{:align => "center", :valign => "top"}
							%table#email-footer{:bgcolor => "#403e37", :width => "100%", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "border-spacing:0;border-collapse: collapse;"}
								%tr
									%td{:align => "right", :valign => "top"}
										%p{:style => "color:#fff;font-family: 'HelveticaNeue-Light', 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:10px;"}
											FIND US ON:
											%a{:href => "http://www.facebook.com/get.ruuted", :style => "color:#fff;margin-left:10px"}
												%img{:src => "https://d2q0qd5iz04n9u.cloudfront.net/_ssl/proxy.php/http/uruut-dev.herokuapp.com/assets/email-facebook.png", :style => "vertical-align:middle;margin:3px;"} /get.ruuted
											%a{:href => "http://www.twitter.com/uruut", :style => "color:#fff;margin-left:10px"}
												%img{:src => "https://d2q0qd5iz04n9u.cloudfront.net/_ssl/proxy.php/http/uruut-dev.herokuapp.com/assets/email-twitter.png", :style => "vertical-align:middle;margin:3px;"} @uruut
					